These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: trance, indie, gospel, house, techno, electronic
6 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, pony, frog, hamster, chinchilla
 1. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the fan of indie##5
 3. the fan of techno is not the owner of the hamster##6
 4. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the fan of indie##5
 5. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
 6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
 7. the owner of the hamster is not the fan of indie##6
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of trance is somewhere between the owner of the chinchilla and the fan of house##7
10. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
12. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
13. the owner of the dog is the fan of trance##1
14. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5
15. the fan of electronic is the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | house   | trance | gospel   | electronic     | indie    | techno   |
| Pet           | hamster | dog   | chinchilla | frog | pony | lizard |

