.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, sports, mystery, satire, adventure, zombie
6 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, frog, horse, ferret, rabbit
 1. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching sports movies##5
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 7. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching adventure movies is not the owner of the ferret##6
10. the owner of the goat is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the horse##7
11. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
12. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
13. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
14. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
15. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
16. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
17. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the owner of the goldfish and the person watching adventure movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | zombie | satire | adventure     | mystery      | comedy |
| Pet           | goldfish         | frog        | ferret   | horse | goat | rabbit    |

