.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, iced-tea, almond-milk, coffee, milk
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: ice-hockey, milk-polo, rugby, soccer, handball, cricket
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 4. the person who's sport is milk-polo is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
 5. the person drinking juice is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is milk-polo is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
10. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking sprite##7
11. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
13. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
14. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | coffee        | almond-milk | milk    | juice    | iced-tea | sprite |
| Sport      | milk-polo | handball  | cricket | soccer | ice-hockey | rugby      |

