12. the person driving the bike is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the person driving the helicopter##7
13. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Pet         | hedgehog   | hamster | mouse      | frog | pony  | goat   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | car  | helicopter | taxi   | bike | roller |

