.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: rock-climbing, singing, magic-tricks, puzzles, cooking, sudoku
The people have 6 different jobs:  social-worker, chef, security-guard, electrician, police-officer, nurse
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the electrician and the chef##7
 5. the nurse is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the police-officer##1
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the electrician##5
 8. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 9. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5
10. the chef is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
11. the nurse is on the right of the security-guard##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the electrician##5
13. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
14. the chef is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
15. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks         | puzzles | singing | rock-climbing   | sudoku | cooking  |
| Job     | police-officer | electrician  | security-guard  | nurse | chef  | social-worker |

 